title: Hands Up Legacy Eternity
description:
Hands Up Legacy is a movement, a symbol under which all Hands Up fans and producers can unite.

We fight to keep Hands Up strong and beating and with the combined efforts of all producers involved we have achieved that, and will so for many years to come. Show your support for Hands Up Legacy by sharing it everywhere, help us grown stronger!

Would you like to be a part of Hands Up Legacy's next album? Send me a message!
